      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Why ING Is Strategically Dominant</h2>

      <p>The -ING suffix holds a unique position in Scrabble strategy because it combines three separate tactical advantages into one holding pattern.</p>

