          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Stack parallel ING words:</span> Playing an -ING word parallel to an existing word can create multiple 2-letter crosswords simultaneously, racking up points from each intersection.</p>
        </div>
