      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">ING Bingo Strategy — The 50-Point Play</h2>

      <p>The -ING suffix is your clearest path to bingo plays. When you hold I, N, G alongside balanced consonants and vowels, you should actively hunt for 7-letter plays before settling for shorter words.</p>

