          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 tiles</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Needed alongside ING</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>The best companion tiles for ING bingos are common letters like E, R, S, T, A, and L. Combinations like ING + REST, ING + TALE, or ING + STAR produce dozens of valid 7-letter words each.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Premium Square Interactions</h2>

      <p>Placing -ING words strategically on the board can multiply your score dramatically. The 3-tile suffix gives you predictable landing positions relative to premium squares.</p>

